reviews.review_text: Incredible show...incredible sound! How can this particular recording not have more listens and reviews? Incredible show and one of the best soundboards (yay Charlie Miller!!) that I've ever heard! Same goes for the previous two Alpine Valley '89 shows. Just amazing...
